## ğŸ” Important Notes

* Make sure youâ€™ve used `password_hash()` when storing passwords:

  ```php
  $hashed = password_hash($newpass, PASSWORD_DEFAULT);
  ```

* All users must be updated with **hashed passwords**. Plain-text wonâ€™t work with `password_verify()`.
